<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 14 at 10:20AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Snow will cause travel difficulties through late this
evening...
Periods of snow will cause minor travel difficulties through this
evening. While generally less than 1 inch accumulation is expected,
localized higher accumulations up to 3 inches along north-facing
slopes are possible. Snow is expected to gradually diminish
through this evening.</description>
